p from friends or a guild. If you don't have time for a Raiding guild, then join a family guild for grouping prospects. The point is, your experience in EQ is one of the few places in your life you will ever really have any serious input into how things turn out... put forth the effort and you will reap the rewards.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
