ined at a much higher level than what they are capable of fighting. Just because you paid for some overpriced utility spells doesn't justify your argument.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;As for the OP's comments, I would have to reiterate previous suggestions to camp DoDH runes. They drop more often and you also have a chance at some other decent loots there that aren't too common in the bazaar yet. I find it funny that in the bazaar that Shadowspine runes are routinely cheaper than Muramite runes as if they have any lesser value. Good luck to in your endeavors :-)&lt;/div&gt;</description>
